# .vibecrafted: track GUIDELINES.md + the plans/reports symlinks (which point
# at the per-day artifact root in $HOME). Ignore everything else (tmp scratch,
# generated prompts, ad-hoc files).
/.vibecrafted/*
!/AGENTS.md
!/.vibecrafted/plans
!/.vibecrafted/reports
